<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge" />
    <title>Grader Welcome Message</title>
    <style>
      body {
        background: #f2f2f2;
      }
      section {
        font-family: proxima-nova, sans-serif;
        margin: auto;
        width: 60%;
      }
      .small_text {
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-top: 30px;
        color: #424242;
      }
      .body_par {
        color: #333;
      }
      .login_body li {
        list-style: none;
      }
      .login_body li {
        color: #333;
      }
      a {
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .footer_text {
        font-size: 15px;
        margin-top: 20px;
        color: #333;
      }
      footer {
        margin-top: 35px;
        color: #222;
        font-size: 15px;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
      }
      footer p {
        line-height: 1.7;
      }
      .logo_img {
        width: 100%;
      }
      @media screen and (max-width: 812px) {
        section {
          width: 95%;
        }
        .small_text {
          font-size: 14px;
          margin-top: 40px;
        }
        .footer_text {
          font-size: 13px;
        }
        .tuner_logo {
          height: 280px;
        }
        .tuner_logo img {
          margin-top: 70px;
          width: 200px;
        }
        .logo_img {
          width: 60%;
          margin: auto;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <section>
      <h2>Grader Account Info.</h2>
      <div class="small_text">
        <div class="logo_img">
          <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/kennylazer/image/upload/v1588333509/logo_nrtjh5.png" alt="grader_logo" />
        </div>
        <p>
          <strong>Dear <%= firstname %> <%= lastname %>,</strong>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="body_par">
        <p>
          Your account on <b>Grader</b> Was successfully created. your were
          registered as <b>'Teacher'</b>. The following are your login
          credentials, We wish you Good luck!
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="login_body">
        <h4>Your Login Credentials</h4>
        <li>
          <b>Email: </b><span class="info_text"><%= email %></span>
        </li>
        <li><b>Password: </b><span class="info_text"><%= genpwd %></span></li>
      </div>
      <p class="footer_text">
        If you encounter any problem, please don't hesitate to CONTACT US at
        <span style="color:#424242"
          ><a href="mailto:info.gsystem1@gmail.com"
            >info.gsystem1@gmail.com</a
          ></span
        >
      </p>
      <footer>
        <p>
          <span>Kigali, Rwanda</span><br />
          <span><b> (+250) 782 815 204</b></span
          ><br />
          <span><b> (+250) 780 199 446</b></span
          ><br />
        </p>
        &copy; Grader - All Rights Reserved.
      </footer>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>